    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Iwwy_yFRaN0m"
      },
      "source": [
        "NOTE: On xGChain and xGBuildup \\\\\n",
        "xGChain --> Calculating xG for possessions that lead to a shot where the player was involved at least once in that possession, **INCLUDING** the final pass or the shot. \\\\\n",
        "xGBuildup --> Calculating xG for possessions that lead to a shot where the player was involved at least once in that possession, **EXCLUDING** the final pass or the shot. \\\\"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
